cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) - The paper deals with the decidability of the optimal reachability problem for priced timed automata, which involves logical reasoning and formal methods. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Priced timed automata have been applied in various scheduling and planning problems, which are common topics in AI. 
3. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - Timed automata are a formalism for modeling and analyzing real-time systems, which is relevant to programming languages. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper involves constructing and implementing algorithms for solving the optimal reachability problem for priced timed automata. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - Timed automata are used to model and analyze real-time systems, which is a topic in systems and control.
